<br>
On the Aviak Island, there are two NPC's - a gnome and a dwarf.  Both conned dubious to me (dark elf, Innoruuk worshipper), but still responded.  <br>
<br>
I first hailed the gnome, who told me a story about hunting goblins and some useless blade he got.  He said to go and ask the dwarf about it.<br>
<br>
This I did - the Dwarf asked me if I was interested in buying the blade - a fine blade covered in runes, he said.  I responded yes, and he told me he doesn't have need of money out here, but if I were to bring him certain items, he would give it to me.<br>
<br>
The items he requested were:<br>
<br>
-A keg of Vox's tail tonic<br>
-A block of permafrost to keep it cool<br>
-Two new rebreathers (tinkered item, I think)<br>
<br>
Does anyone else know of this quest?  If you have any information on the quest or where the items can be found, please post it here.<br>
<br>
As I said, it's probably (most certainly) not for Wizard's, but might yield a fine blade if anyone completes it<br>
<br>
Happy hunting,<br>
Shardul Soulsap<br>
Tallon Zek <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugallenite.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gallenite</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/26/00 10:06 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Well, it's probably not a Wizard quest, but.....</span><hr size=1> You bet.  Part of the warrior epic.<br>
